{"tid":1839082,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"統治者「控制法官職位俸祿，迫使法官唯命是從」凌駕於法律之上 是為「人治」！","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T08:11:29.000Z","uid":167548,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b00adfc78bdb14f2d826a3e8a9d085be05fd90f","tid":1839082,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"法治（英語：rule of law），是與人治相反之概念。與法制不同，法治指以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權</span></strong>為前提和基礎立法，以嚴格依法管治國家為核心，以制約權力為關鍵的社會管理機制、社會活動方式和社會秩序狀態[1]。「法治」與「憲政」緊密相關，其內涵不單是要求所有人民守法，更側重於法律對政府權力的控制和拘束。[2][3][4]<br />\n<br />\n法治意味著每個人都受到法律的約束，包括<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立法者</span></strong>、行政官員和<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法官</span></strong>[1]。在這個意義上，法治與統治者凌駕於法律之上的獨裁、人治相對立。缺乏法治可以在民主國家和專制國家中找到，例如由於忽視或無視法律，如果政府沒有足夠的糾正機制來恢復法律，法治就更容易衰退。<br />\n<br />\n以法治為基礎的國家被稱為法治國。在一個法治國中，國家的力量受制於對當局任意行使公權力的約束，以達到保護公民的權利。法治國里的公民共享以法律為基礎的公民自由，並可以使用法院。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25B2%25BB&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77a%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=316e31cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B3%95%E6%B2%BB</a>"},{"pid":"f9b30afca86812b6cd2ae35b4655f479bbac6056","tid":1839082,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"accae55647d309cb54e1b9fd3a82dace31ef1842","tid":1839082,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"法治意味著每個人都受到法律的約束，包括<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立法者</span></strong>、行政官員和<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法官</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n批評法官唔代表余若薇「大律師」, 馬道立「大法官」所講破壞法治！因為破壞緊法治o既是法官, 一班向不受民意授權o既政府唯命是從, 以雙重標準判處黃絲與藍絲！"},{"pid":"7b804695520672721d7e589fe4dc0874d8877c96","tid":1839082,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"執政者與法官同流合污下操控法庭, 實行政治審判, 違反民意, 便是為 法治已死, 人治當道！"},{"pid":"9bc43a5f6f98c580477206fb919af60d3f476f53","tid":1839082,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf590980449570157278ece646dea359e80948c","tid":1839082,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:29:28.000Z","msg":"DLLM個個掛住支那瘟疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb8058f2e28af134f41fa577f2b36f3b054b2d3","tid":1839082,"uid":295572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我好反感當權者不斷欺騙所以人，話示威者破壞法治，<span style=\"color: red;\">只有當權者才有能力破壞法治。」</span></span>（陳惠源律師）"},{"pid":"2060dd2a4f6b6aa27210a903c563902a97edbbee","tid":1839082,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fb8058f2e28af134f41fa577f2b36f3b054b2d3","tid":1839082,"uid":295572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我好反感當權者不斷欺騙所以人，話示威者破壞法治，<span style=\"color: red;\">只有當權者才有能力破壞法治。」</span></span>（陳惠源律師）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:43:24.000Z","msg":"算 香港人貪生怕死 某程度上場運動行動派已完"},{"pid":"82d5acc72481d561bf98efb1c1615ceba3af542f","tid":1839082,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2060dd2a4f6b6aa27